			<section>
				<h2>FoodieSave goals:</h2>
				<p>

FoodieSave is a web application that in its core functionality, aims to help reduce food waste. It is targeted to "people who cook" in households or who are looking for 
inspiration to prepare a meal from products available at home. The premise of the product is to present a base of recipes with the option of suggesting specific recipes based 
on the provided list of ingredients. On its basis, the website will present meals that can be prepared from the owned products. Current version of service offers just some basic 
functionality related to finding recipes and add them to favorites. This functionality still needs some more work, but we hope it will change soon. 

				</p>
			</section>

