			<section>
				<h2>Description:</h2>
				<p>

This website is our final project for Digital Product class and has purely educational purposes for us. 
It was an opportunity for each of us to develop our skills and learn something new. We acquired more knowledge about using the <a href="https://nodejs.org/">Node.js</a> and <a href="https://expressjs.com/">Express.js</a> framework. 
And also about the use of No-SQL databases such as <a href="https://www.mongodb.com/">MongoDB</a> and processing data from external APIs.<br><br>

The technologies and some tools used to construct this site are listed in the section below.<br><br>

The information pertinent to the recipes shown on this website, such as recipe names, descriptions, ingredients, 
ingredient images, and preparing instructions, are fetched from the <a href="https://spoonacular.com/food-api">Spoonacular</a> food and recipes API.<br><br>

<b class="text-danger">This website was built with the only purposes of learning and entertainment. We do not recommend you to prepare any food based on the recipes presented here. Not right now.</b><br><br>

				</p>
